    "description": "Might is Right是一款老式回合制策略游戏，它具有简单的操作控制和复杂的深层机制。<br>在游戏里，你控制最多可由6人组成的、以你的英雄为首的小队，行走于无疆天地，战斗于广袤世界。<br>每个角色都在战斗中获得经验，并据此升级。每个级别都有一个天赋点供使用。每个角色都有自己的天赋树，可组合出许多迥异独特的风格——从玻璃火炮魔法师到肉身坦克治疗师。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/bf3335b5640f1ad0066aa8a489da74ca.avif?t=1653596070\" width=600 height=259 /></span><br>游戏提供两种已经熟知的模式供切换：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探险模式</h2>此模式下，你的小队能够在地图上自由移动，收集珍宝，访问据点及执行任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/6380ca24369971c60c79dba20f59d720.poster.avif?t=1653596070\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/6380ca24369971c60c79dba20f59d720.webm?t=1653596070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/6380ca24369971c60c79dba20f59d720.mp4?t=1653596070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/2d3ad2f748eabd2cf708707adfc53aef.poster.avif?t=1653596070\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/2d3ad2f748eabd2cf708707adfc53aef.webm?t=1653596070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1152160/extras/2d3ad2f748eabd2cf708707adfc53aef.mp4?t=1653596070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗模式</h2>在探险模式下与敌方小队交手时，将自动进入战斗模式。此模式下，你将与敌人进行回合大战，直至分出胜负。当然如果战况告急，你可以随时选择逃离。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i